          "title": "Mission: Impossible – Dead Reckoning Part One",
          "year": 2023,
          "note": "McQuarrie's third MI and ninth collaboration with Cruise. All three loved it: the funniest of the series, close to silent comedy in the Fiat chase, and John Wick-adjacent in the Venice sword fight. The villain is the Entity, an AI, played out through Gabriel (Esai Morales) and Paris (Pom Klementieff); Hayley Atwell joins as Grace, plus the returning Ilsa (Rebecca Ferguson), Luther, Benji, and the White Widow (Vanessa Kirby). Amanda found the AI plot muddled and the Gabriel-as-Ethan's-past retcon a reach; all agreed the split-in-two runtime shows, but the train and motorcycle-cliff set pieces are the reason to go."
        }
      ]
